 ARRAY['Fill a highball glass to the brim with ice.','Pour gin over ice.','Pour tonic water slowly down the side of the glass to preserve carbonation.','Squeeze lime over, drop in.','Stir once, gently.','Garnish with juniper berries if using.'],
 2,0,1,145,0,10,0,0,8,5),

